Package: d3r
Type: Package
Title: d3r: Data-Driven Documents (D3) for the R Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jacek", "Pardyak",
      email = "jacek.pardyak@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: d3r is an R package designed to seamlessly integrate D3.js into your R environment, enabling dynamic and interactive data visualizations. Whether you're working in RStudio, Shiny, Quarto, Jupyter, Selenium, or plain HTML, d3r provides an easy way to create, embed, and interact with D3.js-based charts, graphs, and visualizations without needing deep JavaScript knowledge.
